OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBen Stiller: Actor speaks  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fabout 'distressing' scenes 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fon visit to Ukraine        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, US actor Ben Stiller has described the 
OL,6, scenes in war-torn Ukraine as          
OL,7, "distressing", "shocking" and on a     
OL,8, bigger scale than any movie.           
OL,10,FStiller met President Volodymyr        
OL,11,FZelensky in Ukraine's capital Kyiv, in 
OL,12,Fhis role as goodwill ambassador for the
OL,13,FUnited Nations refugee agency (UNHCR). 
OL,15,FThe Hollywood star told Zelensky that  
OL,16,Fhe was his hero, and complimented his  
OL,17,Fprevious acting career.                
OL,19,F"It's my first time coming to an area  
OL,20,Fthat's in conflict," he told the BBC.  
